"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1933044-Josh-Kerr-Jakob-Ingebrigtsen-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Middle-distance superstar Jakob Ingebrigtsen was forced to eat his words at theOlympicson Tuesday night after losing out to Josh Kerr by two positions in the 1500m final.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28, \"end\": 46, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jakob Ingebrigtsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Norwegian previously stated that he could beat the British athlete 'blindfolded'.\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 177, \"end\": 186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.995111338999309, \"rank\": 0.004016568755711482, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9985846271291049, \"rank\": 0.0008334706850104265, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ingebrigtsen and Kerr's big showdown was a long time in the making.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair have been trading blows on and off the track for years, with both parties playing up the rivalry in the build-up to the Paris Olympics and making it clear that there is little love between them.\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Kerr got the better of Ingebrigtsen at the Diamond League meeting in Eugene back in May, the Edinburgh-born runner took a break from competing in the 1500m, instead switching his attention to the 800m.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.999999995881808, \"rank\": 4.117975209142915e-09, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is difficult to refer to him as a rival when he is never there,\\\" Ingebrigtsen prodded.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He is known as the Brit who never competes.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I try to enter as many races as I can and I want to be here to entertain.\\\"\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This wasn't the end of the fighting talk though.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Kerr set the indoor two-mile world record at the Millrose Games back in February, Ingebrigtsen stated: \\\"I would have beaten him in that race, blindfolded.\\\"\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, attention has been focused on their showdown in Paris.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.9176486074121884e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the stage set for an all-time classic at the Stade de France, Ingebrigtsen imposed a blistering early pace.\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old turned the screw as the likes of Kerr and Timothy Cheruiyot clung on behind him.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timothy_Cheruiyot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Timothy Cheruiyot\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timothy_Cheruiyot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timothy_Cheruiyot\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the ferocious start proved costly for the reigning 5000m Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1636, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.9176486074121884e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9999671133642468, \"rank\": 3.288765946743896e-05, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the field rounded onto the home straight on the final lap, Kerr snatched the lead on the outside.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ingebrigtsen moved across to block his rival's advance but had nothing left in the tank.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That defensive move opened the door for Team USA's Cole Hocker, who thrust himself into the picture with a perfect kick.\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2034, \"end\": 2042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.46694705197408815, \"rank\": 0.4662433732770446, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After outsprinting Kerr in the final stretch, Hocker sealed an unlikely gold with Team USA colleague Yared Nuguse snatching the bronze medal with a bold late charge of his own.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.46694705197408815, \"rank\": 0.4662433732770446, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2217, \"end\": 2229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yared Nuguse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit was second; Ingebrigtsen finished an unfathomable fourth.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I opened with a 54-second lap,\\\" Ingebrigtsen confessed.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That wasn't the plan at all.\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was at least two seconds too fast.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was thinking about slowing down, but the next lap was almost the same speed.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I ruined it for myself by going way too hard.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"I felt really strong and I have had a good progression with races this year.\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not realise what pace it actually was.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not the plan to open that hard.\\\"\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 3018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3290, \"end\": 3303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.091978028399248e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\